atermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:573,&quot;width&quot;:812,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:720,&quot;bytes&quot;:132353,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:true,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F44d8699e-ead1-4344-924e-719f81a4984b_812x573.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F44d8699e-ead1-4344-924e-719f81a4984b_812x573.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F44d8699e-ead1-4344-924e-719f81a4984b_812x573.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F44d8699e-ead1-4344-924e-719f81a4984b_812x573.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" fetchpriority="high"></picture></div></a> <polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line><figcaption class="image-caption"><a href="https://twitter.com/StuartMeissner/status/1711095487577616447">斯图尔特·迈斯纳</a>摄</figcaption></figure></div><p>我保证我很快就会回到经济博客，从<a href="https://www.nobelprize.org/prizes/economic-sciences/2023/press-release/">克劳迪娅戈尔丁的诺贝尔奖</a>开始。但首先，关于以色列-哈马斯战争，我还有一件事必须吐露。</p><p>上图来自美国民主社会主义者纽约分会支持巴勒斯坦事业的<a href="https://nypost.com/2023/10/08/nyc-pro-palestinian-rally-slammed-as-abhorrent-as-hamas-attacks-israel/">集会</a>。这次集会是在 10 月 8 日举行的，一天前，一千多名哈马斯枪手<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/October_2023_Gaza%E2%88%92Israel_conflict">袭击了以色列</a>。这是 DSA 当地<a href="https://twitter.com/Nowooski/status/1711228710127624514">分会</a>在全国各地以及各个大学校园举行的许多类似<a href="https://twitter.com/ConnecticutDSA/status/1710977718798397584">集会</a>之一。据报道，照片中的女子向亲以色列的反抗议者展示了纳粹党徽。</p><p>如果您还没有读到全部内容，哈马斯枪手<a href="https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/2023/10/08/israel-festival-attack-gaza-militants/">袭击了一个音乐节</a>，杀死了<a href="https://twitter.com/visegrad24/status/1711091011982623125">至少 260 名</a>音乐节参加者，并劫持了 <a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2023/10/09/world/middleeast/israel-hostages-hamas-explained.html">数十人作为</a>人质。随后，枪手继续袭击以色列周边城镇，不分青红皂白地<a href="https://twitter.com/AndrewFeinberg/status/1711444450512159006">屠杀</a>平民。迄今为止，哈马斯袭击造成的总遇难人数估计高达<a href="https://www.scmp.com/news/world/middle-east/article/3237210/hundreds-dead-israel-hamas-war-lebanons-hezbollah-launches-attacks">1000 名以色列人</a>，不过随着更多尸体的发现，这一数字可能还会上升。<a href="https://twitter.com/MattGertz/status/1711784332543627549">婴儿</a>被发现<a href="https://twitter.com/hxhassan/status/1711828903210209448">被烧伤</a>。视频显示哈马斯<a href="https://www.washingtonpost.com/investigations/2023/10/09/israel-hamas-hostage-death/">屠杀了</a>一些被劫持的人质。哈马斯在受害者的 Facebook 页面上<a href="https://twitter.com/visegrad24/status/1711513305854943442">发布了</a>一些现场直播的处决视频。还有大量关于哈马斯战士<a href="https://www.thejc.com/news/israel/girls-raped-next-to-their-dead-friends-at-rave-massacre-4OQOewv0ezTxkKPOCxVzTV">强奸</a>和<a href="https://www.theatlantic.com/international/archive/2023/10/kidnappings-israel-hamas-photographs/675593/">其他虐待行为</a>的报道。受害者中有<a href="https://www.cnn.com/2023/10/09/politics/americans-israel-gaza/index.html">11 名美国人</a>，以及参加过该节日或在该节日工作过的<a href="https://www.hindustantimes.com/world-news/israelpalestine-latest-foreigners-killed-in-israel-hamas-war-include-us-french-thai-citizens-101696866423018.html">其他国家</a>的公民。</p><p>这种行为在任何战争中都会被理所当然地谴责为战争罪。我是乌克兰的坚定支持者，但如果乌克兰突击队屠杀了俄罗斯音乐节，我会严厉谴责，并要求乌克兰政府确保不再发生这种情况。但许多举行亲巴勒斯坦集会的美国左翼人士兴高采烈地庆祝以平民为目标的解放行为，甚至拿谋杀开玩笑。例如，<a href="https://twitter.com/BGOnTheScene/status/1711145162657673347">您可以观看一段视频</a>，其中纽约集会上的一位演讲者说道：</p><blockquote><p>正如您可能已经看到的那样，他们在某种狂欢或沙漠派对中度过了一段愉快的时光，直到抵抗运动出现了电动悬挂式滑翔机并带走了至少数十名时髦人士。</p></blockquote><p>观众为他对暴行的描述喝彩，欢呼雀跃。与此同时，其他集会的海报<a href="https://twitter.com/bswagspeare/status/1711528099954012636">上装饰着</a>哈马斯袭击者用来攻击节日的滑翔伞的英雄形象。一些章节<a href="https://twitter.com/Nowooski/status/1711624199830462965">明确赞扬了</a>这些攻击。</p><p>与此同时，在其他国家，集会更加血腥。<a href="https://twitter.com/AustralianJA/status/1711501583295680694">这是一段来自澳大利亚悉尼的视频</a>，视频中人们高呼“用毒气杀死犹太人！”</p><p>在网上，支持攻击的左派言论得到了大量的认可和参与： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F760b3c5b-1534-403d-8396-46739499022a_904x207.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F760b3c5b-1534-403d-8396-46739499022a_904x207.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F760b3c5b-1534-403d-8396-46739499022a_904x207.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F760b3c5b-1534-403d-8396-46739499022a_904x207.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F760b3c5b-1534-403d-8396-46739499022a_904x207.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3