ef="https://medium.com/@gravity7/ukraine-lets-talk-tankie-f6820da850ef">人</a><a href="https://www.theatlantic.com/politics/archive/2019/03/bernie-sanderss-new-speechwriter-has-controversial-past/585547/">大多数</a>都是外人，这是有<a href="https://theintercept.com/2022/05/03/ohio-primary-elections-nina-turner-shontel-brown/">充分理由的</a>。在对民主党的敌意收购<a href="https://www.brookings.edu/articles/why-bernie-sanders-vastly-underperformed-in-the-2020-primary/">失败</a>后，伯尼的一些支持者只是加入了更广泛的进步运动，但也有一些人留在了他们创建的左翼媒体生态系统中，只是继续谴责拜登政府。</p><p>这一切都是毫无意义和烦人的。正如拜登政府的政策所表明的那样，引发新社会主义和伯尼·桑德斯竞选活动的不满情绪<em>最终</em>确实推动民主党走向进步的方向。但最终成功的推动者是沃伦派进步人士，他们闭门争论自己的想法。伯尼和他的人民有机会在美国发起一场真正的草根平等运动，但他们搞砸了。</p><p>但导致推动社会主义运动的民众能量爆发的问题并没有消失。昂贵的医疗保健、不平等、高额学生债务和气候变化仍然是主要问题。尽管伯尼的竞选团队采取了极端的想法，以区别于沃伦和拜登，但社会主义者认可的一些基本方法在方向上与有效解决这些问题的明智政策相似。</p><p>因此，这里有伯尼的四个想法的一些更现实的版本——全民医疗保险、财富税、学生债务取消和绿色新政——我认为它们实际上会起作用。</p><h4>对于全民医疗保健，请使用像日本这样的系统</h4><p>大家都知道美国的医疗费用太高了。我们将 GDP 的 17% 左右用于医疗保健，而其他富裕国家——包括比我们富裕的新加坡和瑞士——的支出要少得多。 </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0c21b597-5eda-4a2a-bf63-3cc1bdee635f_1020x720.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0c21b597-5eda-4a2a-bf63-3cc1bdee635f_1020x720.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0c21b597-5eda-4a2a-bf63-3cc1bdee635f_1020x720.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0c21b597-5eda-4a2a-bf63-3cc1bdee635f_1020x720.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0c21b597-5eda-4a2a-bf63-3cc1bdee635f_1020x720.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0c21b597-5eda-4a2a-bf63-3cc1bdee635f_1020x720.png" width="684" height="482.8235294117647" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/0c21b597-5eda-4a2a-bf63-3cc1bdee635f_1020x720.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:720,&quot;width&quot;:1020,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:684,&quot;bytes&quot;:142179,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0c21b597-5eda-4a2a-bf63-3cc1bdee635f_1020x720.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0c21b597-5eda-4a2a-bf63-3cc1bdee635f_1020x720.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0c21b597-5eda-4a2a-bf63-3cc1bdee635f_1020x720.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0c21b597-5eda-4a2a-bf63-3cc1bdee635f_1020x720.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></figure></div><p>当然，这会增加美国患者的痛苦，包括高昂的自付费用。正如我将解释的那样，国民健康保险将是解决这个问题的一个好方法。但伯尼党人把支持国民健康保险的<em>理由</em>放在了错误的位置上，这导致他们制定了一个行不通的计划。</p><p>首先，社会主义者关注自付费用，承诺完全消除这些费用。但自付费用已经只占美国人医疗总支出的一小部分——事实上，比包括英国在内的几乎任何其他富裕国家都要小。 </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9f5d466c-968d-4998-b9de-cedbbe5b374d_1020x720.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9f5d466c-968d-4998-b9de-cedbbe5b374d_1020x720.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9f5d466c-968d-4998-b9de-cedbbe5b374d_1020x720.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9f5d466c-968d-4998-b9de-cedbbe5b374d_1020x720.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9f5d466c-968d-4998-b9de-cedbbe5b374d_1020x720.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_145